外观上区别 1. 脖颈：鹅脖子修长，鸭脖子短粗。 2. 额头：多数鹅头顶有肉瘤，鸭子没有。 3. 嘴巴：鹅嘴宽长、颜色偏橙黄；鸭嘴扁短，多 为黄色或黑灰色。 4. 体型：鹅整体更大更壮，体态挺拔；鸭子偏小，身形圆润。 习性 & 叫声 叫声：鹅叫声洪亮高昂，鸭子叫声清脆短促。 性格：鹅警惕性强、好斗护领地；鸭子温顺胆小。 走路：鹅步伐稳健从容；鸭子走路摇摆幅度更大。 简单速记: 长脖有肉瘤、叫声洪亮是鹅；短脖无肉瘤、叫声细碎是鸭。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1ac5037841cd478ad6d9a25577edddc1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2049562215062172314"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI5cnZ69jJ9McMEAMaCTExOTk3NjkxNCDvirrRBjAAOGJAHHITMjA0OTU2MjIxNTA2MjE3MjMxNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1782339489.123261", "card_id": "Q_2005254307231074086", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "现在的孩子肚子里很少有寄生虫的原因是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "记得小时候肚子里经常有虫子，语言喝药打虫，现在的孩子只听过喝药补钙铁锌，没听过喝药打虫"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-efe4f3dfb42422968a7b29ed9e337fbe.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2005254307231074086"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI5cnZ69jJ9McMEAMaCTExODQwODk1NiD6qLXMBjAAOMoBQB1yEzIwMDUyNTQzMDcyMzEwNzQwODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "2053249682965534313", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2053071755242103665", "title": "世界杯小组赛：苏格兰 vs 巴西", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMjA1MzI0OTY4Mjk2NTUzNDMxM3ITMjA1MzI0OTY4Mjk2NTUzNDMxM3gA", "tag": "讨论", "tag_bg_color": "GYL01A"}, {"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.z